# Polish ICS UI & Administrative Experience

This plan aims to finalize the "command center" feel of the application by replacing remaining mock elements with real-time dynamic data and ensuring the public portal is comprehensive.

## User Review Required

> [!NOTE]
> The Dashboard chart will now show actual crossing activity from the database rather than a fixed daily curve. If there is no activity in the last 24h, it will appear flat.

