## Open Questions

- Should the dashboard chart only show "Cleared" crossings, or all activity including "Flagged" ones?
- For the public "Information" page, should we include a downloadable PDF of the official ICS regulations?

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Browser subagent will log in and verify that the header displays the correct Agent Name.
- Browser subagent will log out and verify it returns to the login screen and cannot navigate back to `/admin`.
- Browser subagent will verify that a newly added crossing appears in the "Latest Activity" (if applicable).

### Manual Verification
- Verify the responsive behavior of the new Information page content.
- Ensure uploaded photos (if any) are correctly rendered in the Traveler Search.
